-Entities
------------------------
   - User
   - Message
   - Room

-Events
---------------------------------
   - User --> User (Chat)
   - User --> Room (Subscribe)
   - User --> Room (Unsubscribe)
   - User --> Room (Chat)


-Bots
---------------------------------
    - UserBot - Responsible for
             --> Sending chat events to other user bots
             --> Listening to chat events from other user bots
             --> Listening to chat events from Rooms
